snippet.title: AMBER HEARD Coming to the MCU as Sue Storm in FANTASTIC FOUR?!
snippet.description:
📢 NEW ENAMEL PINS on Pre-Order HERE - http://www.shopclownfish.com
Amber Heard is rumored to be eying up the role of Sue Storm (aka Invisible Woman) in the MCU version of Fantastic Four. She's also rumored to be getting a standalone Mera film. Regardless of whether or not these rumors turn out to be true, it's already clear that her career is in a much better place than her ex Johnny Depp's is. Depp was recently fired by Warner Bros., but Heard's role as Mera seems safe and secure... for now.
